---
import Button from '@/components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<section class="bio">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <p class="bio__text">
      I'm a protocol and infrastructure lead with a background in distributed systems, proofs,
      real-time ML, and applied cryptography. I've worked across secure SCIF environments and
      decentralized networks, translated research into operational systems, and built public writing
      around the deeper civilizational questions these systems raise. I also come out of a parallel
      life in music and education, which continues to shape how I think about structure, pattern, and
      coordination.
    </p>
    <div class="bio__ctas">
      <Button href="/about" variant="text">About Jason &rarr;</Button>
      <Button href="/resume" variant="text">Resume &rarr;</Button>
      <Button href="/contact" variant="text">Contact &rarr;</Button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .bio {
    padding-block: var(--sp-16);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-line);
  }

  .bio__text {
    font: var(--text-body-lg);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    max-width: 42em;
  }

  .bio__ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--sp-6);
    margin-top: var(--sp-6);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
